print("Q4")
conditions = [
    (survey["age"] >= 18) & (survey["age"] < 25),
    (survey["age"] >= 25) & (survey["age"] < 40),
    (survey["age"] >= 40) & (survey["age"] < 55),
    (survey["age"] >= 55)
             ]
values = ['18-25', '25-40', '40-55','55+']
survey["age_group"] = np.select(conditions, values)
